				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Repro steps:\r\n1. Start the game.\r\n2. peace\r\n3. loadlevel WLD_Main_A\r\n4. goto 126.053; 45.243; -227\r\n5. create OBJ_Oil_Of_The_Basilisk\r\n6. Apply it on the petrified drow\r\n7. Ctrl Shift K the Spectator (if he's attacking you)\r\n8. Speak to the Drow"
				},
